room_title: Escape room "Escape from the Office" by Can You Escape? in Tampa
room_description:
What could be your worst day? You’re working late, everyone leaves and then boom - your door shuts and locks. Trapped in with no signs of escape, you must rally your team to solve puzzles scattered throughout the seemingly ordinary space. How on earth will you get out?
The difficulty level is adjustable and can vary from beginner to expert.
